GS&F Lunch & Learn notes:

INSTALL WORDPRESS:

Run docker app

cd ~/project/LNL

https://www.digitalocean.com/community/questions/docker-compose-for-wp-and-phpmyadmin

INIT from command line: `docker-compose up` or `docker-compose up -d` for detached mode.

#####
http://localhost:8181 to view phpmyadmin
username: wordpress
password: wordpress


http://localhost:8000 to begin wp install

Update wp core to latest
Update Themes to latest

Activate twentyseventeen theme

Customize -> Homepage Settings -> Homepage = Home, Posts page = Blog


Install Sniglet plugin
-----------------------

cd projects/lnl_wp/wp-content/plugins

git clone https://github.com/hawkwynd/sniglets.git (hawkwynd / Sc00tre1)

http://localhost:8000/wp-admin/plugins.php

Activate Sniglet plugin

Edit wp-content/themes/twentyseventeen/template-parts/page/content-front-page.php

Change code to add the random sniglet call at line +- 42:

                     <h2>The Daily Sniglet</h2>

                   				<?php
                                   sniglet_random();

                   					/* translators: %s: Name of current post */

                   					the_content(
                   						sprintf(
                   							__( 'Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> "%s"</span>', 'twentyseventeen' ),
                   							get_the_title()
                                               )
                   					);

Save and browse to home page to see the sniglet load a random entry from the database into the page.



